                                          not  = zero
                     go to acc-cbp-pgf-600.
           move      "Manca il sottoconto contabile per c/c associato al
      -              " codice banca  "    to   w-err-box-err-msg      .
           perform   box-msg-err-000      thru box-msg-err-999        .
           go to     acc-cbp-pgf-100.
       acc-cbp-pgf-530.
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Se tipo operazione : 1630               *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Sottoconto contabile associato      *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           move      w-let-arc-cbp-cco    to   w-tes-cbp-pgf-stc (1)  .
