      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Valore impostato in campo di destinazione       *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      v-num                to   w-exp-sel-tsf-inx      .
           if        w-exp-sel-tsf-inx    =    zero           or
                     w-exp-sel-tsf-inx    >    w-exp-sel-tsf-num
                     move  zero           to   w-tes-sel-tsf (1)
                     go to acc-sel-tsf-400.
           move      w-exp-sel-tsf-vel
                    (w-exp-sel-tsf-inx)   to   w-tes-sel-tsf (1)      .
