      *              * l'indice per un solo tipo scadenza              *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      w-tes-sel-tsf (1)    to   w-vis-sel-tpm-inx      .
           if        w-vis-sel-tpm-inx    >    2 or
                     w-vis-sel-tpm-inx    =    zero
