      *              * Data scadenza                                   *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           perform   vis-dts-scf-000      thru vis-dts-scf-999        .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Importo scadenza                                *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           perform   vis-imp-scf-000      thru vis-imp-scf-999        .
