           move      rf-sfs-trs-scf       to   w-rig-trs-scf (1)      .
           move      rf-sfs-tvl-scf       to   w-rig-tvl-scf (1)      .
           move      rf-sfs-tip-ddr       to   w-rig-tip-ddr (1)      .
           move      rf-sfs-num-ddr       to   w-rig-num-ddr (1)      .
